      • addTrackable

        void addTrackable(VuforiaTrackable trackable)
        Adds a trackable on which this VuforiaTrackable.Listener is listening. May not be called once tracking has begun. If the VuforiaTrackable.Listener is already listening to this trackable, then the call has no effect.
